long-range order featuring columns of parallel spins\nin the 'ab' plane and antiparallel spins along 'c' is verified experimentally\nand confirmed by the microscopic analysis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 10 Apr 2012 22:05:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Jul 2012 16:01:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-07-09"}
