form measure and for the dimension conditional measure. The later\nmeasure has closer relation to random generation of structures and is more\n\"generous\" with respect to satisfiability of extension axioms.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Apr 2012 14:25:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-04-12"}
